{
  "title": "Delicious Light Jamaican Chicken Stir fry",
  "description": "A nutty and light Jamaican dish featuring gherkin relish, perfect for a brunch mood, this stir fry is egg-free-friendly and packed with flavor. It combines the warmth of Jamaican spices with the crunch of fresh vegetables.",
  "cuisine": "Jamaican",
